0713458941_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mBrPwxcF6iMQ7kNvgFIeNkj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AOCINpy1rnKm2Ls2vbPrA30&oh=00_AYAAzM38qULPsqEcbykYO30yDgzKFWKFhVET3b0Dm4XK5Q&oe=66EEB8C7"}, {"file_name": "305.png", "id": "1253018791979472", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031631_1253018795312805_7116269350022562735_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZzE9cQJzqD4Q7kNvgETNB7S&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AOCINpy1rnKm2Ls2vbPrA30&oh=00_AYBjAiPX4aYAUQTBCfZpOcdvkzrst-t5k-cbXOuuyHTCEQ&oe=66EEC4CE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Cream Soda Club", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Gameplay\nWhenever your patrons have enjoyed the show, they \u2018like\u2019 your club. Spend likes as a resource to furnish and develop the venue, and make sure to create a unique atmosphere. Earn more likes to unlock more music tracks and customize your nightspot.\n\nKey features\n- Cream Soda tracks as game levels. Objects in the club react to the beat, turning the game into a music video. \n- Nightclub as the game world. Purchase and place disco balls, speakers, projectors, poufs, and other furnishings.\n- Patron is the law. Some want to dance, some want to eat, and others come to socialize. Your task is to cater to everyone\u2019s needs.\n- Interact with Cream Soda band members as game characters and upgrade their DJ equipment.\n- Sync up with Cream Soda\u2019s music!\n", "short_description": "Cream Soda Club transports you into the world of EDM and parties. Play as an event manager: furnish the club and throw parties with Cream Soda."}]}, "developer_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/privacy_policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], 